                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        Minister <persName type="to">Finch</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-04-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 17, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(As the Department would greatly regret if complications arose from the seizure
                    of the Canadian schooner <hi rend="italic">Agnes G. Donahoe</hi> by the
                    Uruguayan authorities, Mr. Loomis instructs Mr. Finch to use all proper
                    endeavors to bring about peaceable and friendly settlement of the controversy
                    between Uruguay and Great Britain.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
